Please be assured we've passed your valued feedback on to the relevant teams.", 'modified': '2020-06-01T16:05:31Z'}

{'id': 15986994, 'body': "I appreciate that it might be frustrating and I will pass your concerns to the relevant team about this.

But remember, you’ll never have to pay to message people that you've already matched with!

Do let us know if you have any other questions or feedback and we’ll try our best to help.", 'modified': '2020-06-15T08:48:58Z'}

{'id': 20886715, 'body': "We're all about being open and honest, that's why all profile photos will be shown to everyone. 

This means you'll no longer have access to Private Photos albums, as they no longer align with our App and our pledge to Date Honestly.

Thank you for being a valued member of Badoo.", 'modified': '2021-02-05T17:23:36Z'}

{'id': 24268076, 'body': 'Hey there! Badoo will always champion diversity which means that we have a wide range of users using our platform. We work very hard to ensure that everyone is welcome, and will never exclude certain users based on individual preferences - we feel that these types of filters would not align with our beliefs 💜

We also do allow our users to change their location - this is so people can make connections before a move or holiday. You can also turn your GPS off and manually enter your location for more accurate results!

If you have any further questions or would like to discuss anything further, feel free to reach out to us on social media @BadooHelp', 'modified': '2021-08-02T16:08:26Z'}

{'id': 5315124, 'body': 'Credits are only used when you select a feature that requires credits to activate. 

To assist you with any billing issues on your account, we kindly request that you contact us on badoo.com/feedback.

 This will allow us to bring up your details and get back to you as quickly as possible.', 'modified': '2018-10-01T18:23:58Z'}

